{"word":"θακέω","slug":"θακέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θακέω</b></el> <el>(θᾱκέω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θᾶκος'><el>θᾶκος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to sit</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>θακοῦντι παγκρατεῖς ἕδρας</el> <i>sitting on</i> imperial throne, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>: suppliants, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}